  "detailed_description": "<h1>gameplay</h1><p>游戏开始时，能够选择喜欢的角色作为初始角色，也可以碰碰运气选择随机<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123310/extras/04243fc3f7b235ca2d23cff5489d7928.poster.avif?t=1763988746\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123310/extras/04243fc3f7b235ca2d23cff5489d7928.webm?t=1763988746\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123310/extras/04243fc3f7b235ca2d23cff5489d7928.mp4?t=1763988746\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>当拥有请神令后，也可以使用获得更多的角色，游戏中的角色多大数百名<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123310/extras/c448a7305cc41f82d2ff0d0113532369.poster.avif?t=1763988746\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123310/extras/c448a7305cc41f82d2ff0d0113532369.webm?t=1763988746\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123310/extras/c448a7305cc41f82d2ff0d0113532369.mp4?t=1763988746\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>获得未鉴定的装备时使用将会获得6种质量，数百种不同的技能、词条，构筑的装备<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123310/extras/26a381c7f8f3ab505cd7d377bc09f60f.poster.avif?t=1763988746\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123310/extras/26a381c7f8f3ab505cd7d377bc09f60f.webm?t=1763988746\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123310/extras/26a381c7f8f3ab505cd7d377bc09f60f.mp4?t=1763988746\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>当有了新的角色并经过战斗获得灵气后，即可对角色进行升级，哪怕是相同的角色也会有完全不同的成长<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123310/extras/5b128606b971d55696bdd1901cb3ddae.poster.avif?t=1763988746\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123310/extras/5b128606b971d55696bdd1901cb3ddae.webm?t=1763988746\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123310/extras/5b128606b971d55696bdd1901cb3ddae.mp4?t=1763988746\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>如果对角色的神通技能不满意，也可以通过使用神通书来进行替换或新增<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123310/extras/b70399b6d55135df01bb55809c0a455a.poster.avif?t=1763988746\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123310/extras/b70399b6d55135df01bb55809c0a455a.webm?t=1763988746\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123310/extras/b70399b6d55135df01bb55809c0a455a.mp4?t=1763988746\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>若拥有较多同名的角色请神令，也可以通过分解获得材料或者重生角色来提高属性<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123310/extras/4cad208a5c2dc476ca3cfaa9a9606278.poster.avif?t=1763988746\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123310/extras/4cad208a5c2dc476ca3cfaa9a9606278.webm?t=1763988746\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123310/extras/4cad208a5c2dc476ca3cfaa9a9606278.mp4?t=1763988746\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>两个完全不同的角色间也可以进行融合，取长补短，技能组合，当然，若是运气较差也可能一无所有<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123310/extras/131ec171a9ac300fd52e1445ab6c6fe5.poster.avif?t=1763988746\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123310/extras/131ec171a9ac300fd52e1445ab6c6fe5.webm?t=1763988746\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123310/extras/131ec171a9ac300fd52e1445ab6c6fe5.mp4?t=1763988746\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>当拥有多个角色后，可以选择将角色上阵，如果有强力的阵法也会对阵容有着极大的加强<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123310/extras/393e7986267da871fc24eaa605d10744.poster.avif?t=1763988746\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123310/extras/393e7986267da871fc24eaa605d10744.webm?t=1763988746\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123310/extras/393e7986267da871fc24eaa605d10744.mp4?t=1763988746\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>不仅仅角色能够升级，提升玩家的境界等级也会极大的加强所有角色<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123310/extras/57463b02e23d0e52860f9639967927ac.poster.avif?t=1763988746\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123310/extras/57463b02e23d0e52860f9639967927ac.webm?t=1763988746\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123310/extras/57463b02e23d0e52860f9639967927ac.mp4?t=1763988746\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>当玩家突破大道等级时不仅能提高角色的等级上限，还能获得大道点，选择三千大道<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123310/extras/6a00f2a13775521b248607e8ddb52664.poster.avif?t=1763988746\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123310/extras/6a00f2a13775521b248607e8ddb52664.webm?t=1763988746\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123310/extras/6a00f2a13775521b248607e8ddb52664.mp4?t=1763988746\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>当拥有强力的角色与阵容时，便可前往论道界面，与其他道友一较高下，当然也无需担心遇到强者大能，因为每一境界都会有独立的论道系统与奖励<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123310/extras/88e76828b0d70b628cc9bf4d1217ec90.poster.avif?t=1763988746\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123310/extras/88e76828b0d70b628cc9bf4d1217ec90.webm?t=1763988746\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123310/extras/88e76828b0d70b628cc9bf4d1217ec90.mp4?t=1763988746\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>如果背包里的道具已满，也可以将道具放入仓库之中<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123310/extras/eb11f705f1859877f6c00a0782b624f9.poster.avif?t=1763988746\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123310/extras/eb11f705f1859877f6c00a0782b624f9.webm?t=1763988746\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123310/extras/eb11f705f1859877f6c00a0782b624f9.mp4?t=1763988746\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>或者将有价值的物品与其他道友自由贸易，买低卖高，囤货居奇，修道不成，做一商人货通诸天亦可<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123310/extras/fb4078f848742b42d7bfa04498c23ca8.poster.avif?t=1763988746\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123310/extras/fb4078f848742b42d7bfa04498c23ca8.webm?t=1763988746\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123310/extras/fb4078f848742b42d7bfa04498c23ca8.mp4?t=1763988746\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>Sorry, the R&D team is not very proficient in English, so there is currently no English version available<br><br><strong>本游戏没有内购！本游戏没有内购！本游戏没有内购！<br>大家且听我狡辩，我主打的一个就是听劝，直接把付费砍掉，直接就是一个联网放置挂机可交易网游<br>请大家给我一个面子……打的轻点……</strong><br><br>交流QQ群：930278060<br>discord群组：<br><br>洪荒：我挂机成圣（以下简称洪荒）不是一款靠名字够长吸引人的游戏，而是一款精心打磨的大型网络策略卡牌放置角色扮演类游戏<br><br>美术风格使用传承几千年的文字所组成，无一不是大师级设计，不在任何地方节省美术资源的使用，在游戏行业遥遥领先。<br><br>游戏题材选择了以网络小说洪荒流做为大世界，融合了世界顶级IP西游记，中国顶级IP封神演义、宝莲灯、白蛇传、聊斋、东游记、倩女幽魂等等，更甚有史诗传记等不下<br>万部内容结合而成，上到盘古、鸿钧，下到法海、小倩应有尽有，说一句“万P史”也不为过。<br>当然……这些借鉴内容里面各种各样脍炙人口的故事我们肯定是一点没有的。<br>洪荒的核心玩法方面，我们充分的借鉴融合了各种出色的游戏设计。<br><br>比如，我们在史诗级游戏“梦幻西游”中借鉴了宠物资质、炼妖、打书、阵法系统，让玩家可以在洪荒中给不同的角色学习不同的神通，融合不同的角色本源提升资质，正<br>所谓我命由我不由天，是神是仙由你说了算，就算是小钻风也有一颗妖族大圣的心。<br><br>再比如，我们在殿堂级游戏“暗黑破坏神”系列中，借鉴了装备鉴定以获得不同质量以及各式各样的词条组合，达到更高更强的阵容，你再也不用担心看着每个装备属性都<br>一样而不知道选啥了，因为不一样你也不知道选啥。<br><br>再再比如，我们还融合了传统MMO的交易、好友、聊天等系统，你可以将获取的道具与其他玩家进行交易，将自己获得的超强角色进行拍卖，你甚至能囤货居奇，然后让<br>自己在高位套牢，损失惨重。<br><br>其他各式各样的玩法，那就更是多的数不胜数……",
